data.description: Discover the enchantment of 1736 Karen Circle, a captivating residence in Bowling Green, KY 42104. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, including two primary bedrooms, this home offers versatility and comfort. The thoughtfully designed floor plan seamlessly connects living spaces, creating an inviting atmosphere filled with natural light.  The kitchen, equipped with modern appliances and stylish cabinetry, is the heart of the home, complemented by a dining area perfect for shared meals and lasting memories. With three and a half bathrooms, including two luxurious ensuites, convenience is paramount.  Step outside to the fully fenced yard, an oasis for relaxation and play. This outdoor space enhances the home's charm and provides a private retreat for enjoyment. Nestled in a sought-after neighborhood near amenities, schools, and parks, 1736 Karen Circle promises a vibrant community and a welcoming ambiance.  This residence is not just a house—it's an opportunity to embrace comfort and style. Schedule a showing today to experience firsthand the allure of 1736 Karen Circle and make it your new home.
